Coming up Tuesday on @realmoney Was Last Week The "Beginning of The End" of the Virtuous Stock Market Cycle? * In typical times, a river is easier to channel than to stop. * But these are not typical investment times. * Given the unusual nature, artificial conditions and

outside influences (Softbank, David Portnoy (@stoolpresidente), Robinhood et al) -- Wednesday may have marked a possible important top in the major market indices for some time to come. * It is clear to me that speculators are not only playing with fire, they’re dancing (with

apologies to Citigroup's Chuck Prince) in the midst of a firestorm. * While I covered nearly all my shorts in Friday's "woosh" lower I remain pessimistic on the market outlook. * I plan to reshort strength if a rally develops over the near term. @jimcramer @tomkeene
